'''亚齐语'''、或'''阿齐语'''，属于[[马来-波利尼西亚语族|马来-波利尼西亚语族]]，是生活于[[印度尼西亚|印度尼西亚]][[苏门答腊|苏门答腊]][[亚齐特别行政区|亚齐特别行政区]]的土生亚齐人的语言<ref name="Gani">{{citation|last = Asyik|first = Abdul Gani|title = The agreement system in Acehnese|year = 1982|journal = Mon–Khmer Studies|volume = 11|pages = 1–33|url = http://www.lc.mahidol.ac.th/Documents/Publication/MKS/11/abdul1982agreement.pdf|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6H8oiewmw?url=http://www.lc.mahidol.ac.th/Documents/Publication/MKS/11/abdul1982agreement.pdf|archivedate = 2013-06-05|accessdate = 2012-02-24}}</ref>，同时也随着亚齐人的后裔迁徙至马来西亚，因此马来西亚的[[吉打|吉打]]州等地也有分布。<ref name="Graham">{{citation|last = Thurgood|first = Graham|title = The Historical Place of Acehnese: The Known and the Unknown|year = 2007|url = http://www.ari.nus.edu.sg/docs%5CAceh-project%5Cfull-papers%5Caceh_fp_grahamthurgood.pdf|accessdate = 2012-02-24|archive-date = 2008-01-19|archive-url = https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20080119135359/http://www.ari.nus.edu.sg/docs/Aceh-project/full-papers/aceh_fp_grahamthurgood.pdf|dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 分类及相关语言 ==
[[File:COLLECTIE_TROPENMUSEUM_Handgeschreven_boek_in_Acehs_schrift_TMnr_2454-4a.jpg|thumb]]
亚齐语属于[[南岛语系|南岛语系]]的[[马来-波利尼西亚语族|马来-波利尼西亚语族]]下的一支，与亚齐语关系最密切的是[[占语|占语]]、[[马来语|马来语]]、[[米南佳保语|米南佳保语]]、[[盖奥语|盖奥语]]和[[巴塔克语|巴塔克语]]。<ref name="Graham"/>

